988166?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews">G-VS2 Excellent</a></strong></td><td>28988166</td><td>$4,020</td><td>~$4,530</td><td>$790 over floor G-VS2 at identical specs. No reason to pay this.</td></tr><tr><td><strong><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28753735?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews">F-VS2 Excellent</a></strong></td><td>28753735</td><td>$4,040</td><td>~$4,550</td><td>F color step up — $810 over G-VS2 for one color grade. Skip in yellow or rose gold.</td></tr><tr><td><strong><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29066204?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews">G-VS2 Excellent</a></strong></td><td>29066204</td><td>$4,220</td><td>~$4,730</td><td>Premium G-VS2 — $990 above floor. Algorithm bait. Stick with $3,230 entry.</td></tr><tr><td><strong><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/13638641?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews">G-VS2 Excellent</a></strong></td><td>13638641</td><td>$4,230</td><td>~$4,740</td><td>Top of G-VS2 range. $1,000 over floor for identical grade. Unjustifiable.</td></tr></tbody></table>

*Setting total adds $510 for Classic Four-Prong Solitaire 14k white gold. See [1 Carat Diamond Engagement Ring guide](https://diamondcritics.com/1-carat-diamond-engagement-ring/) for full 1ct analysis.

