## Pavé Engagement Rings at Blue Nile — Full Catalog Reviewed

[![Blue Nile Pavé Engagement Ring White Gold](/images/bn-ring-500000.avif)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/pave?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)

[![Blue Nile Pavé Engagement Ring White Gold](/images/bn-ring-501680.avif)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/pave?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)

Pavé bands add 0.15–0.40ct of accent diamond weight along the shank. Blue Nile's pavé catalog runs from $1,020 to $2,650 in this setting type. For daily-wear rings, confirm platinum or 18k gold for pavé — 14k gold pavé prongs are adequate but require more frequent maintenance checks.

**[Pavé Crown Solitaire 14K White Gold — $1,020](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/pave-crown-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-311226?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) · Item #311226** · Entry-level pavé. The crown of the basket is set with accent diamonds that extend the sparkle upward around the center stone. Clean execution at this price point — a strong choice for buyers who want some pavé presence without the full-band cost.

**[Pavé Crown Solitaire Platinum — $1,620](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/pave-crown-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-platinum-by-james-allen-item-311228?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) · Item #311228** · Same pavé crown design in platinum. The $600 step up from 14k is worth it for buyers pairing with D–G color centers where color-neutrality matters. Platinum prong security is noticeably better for the crown accent stones.

**[Solo Infinity Diamond Pavé 14K Yellow Gold — $1,300](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/solo-infinity-diamond-pave-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-by-james-allen-item-316159?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) · Item #316159** · The infinity twist shank adds visual interest while the pavé diamonds run along the band. Distinctive profile that photographs dramatically. Yellow gold requires H color minimum — the warm metal amplifies any residual body color below that threshold.

**[Petite Twist Pavé 14K White Gold — $1,200](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-twist-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-10-ct-tw-item-195314?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) · Item #195314** · A twisted pavé shank with 1/10 ct tw accent weight. The subtle twist differentiates this from a straight pavé band at the same price tier — one of the better entry pavé values in Blue Nile's catalog.

**[Petite Micropavé 14K White Gold — $1,325](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-micropave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-10-ct-tw-item-195402?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) · Item #195402** · Micro-sized accent stones set flush into the shank for a refined, barely-there sparkle effect. Correct choice for buyers who want pavé subtlety rather than pavé presence.

**[French Cut Pavé 14K Rose Gold — $1,460](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/french-cut-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-by-james-allen-item-314753?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) · Item #314753** · French-cut pavé uses V-shaped metal between each accent stone, maximizing light exposure to the side stones. The result is more intense accent sparkle than standard U-cut pavé. Rose gold version pairs well with G–I color center stones.

**[Perfect Pavé Diamond 14K Rose Gold — $1,360](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/perfect-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-by-james-allen-item-314963?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) · Item #314963** · A continuous pavé band with consistent stone sizing throughout. The clean, even execution of the accent stone line is what earns the "Perfect" designation — the most uniform pavé execution in Blue Nile's catalog at this price point.

**[Riviera Pavé 14K White Gold — $1,405](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/riviera-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-6-ct-tw-item-195326?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) · Item #195326** · 1/6 ct tw round brilliants in a classic riviera channel. One of Blue Nile's best-selling pavé styles — the clean straight channel line photographs well and wears cleanly over time.

**[Graduated Pavé 14K Rose Gold — $1,630](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/graduated-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-item-315028?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) · Item #315028** · Accent stones increase in size as they approach the center stone, creating a graduated visual flow that naturally draws the eye inward. More design detail than a straight pavé at only $225 more.

**[Cathedral Pavé Crown 14K Yellow Gold — $1,800](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/cathedral-pave-crown-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-by-james-allen-item-315695?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) · Item #315695** · Cathedral arch elevates the center stone for maximum visual presence, with pavé crown accent diamonds adding a second sparkle tier. Best for 1.5ct+ center stones where the elevated display position enhances face-up impact.

**[French Pavé Platinum — $2,140](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/french-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-1-4-ct-tw-item-195271?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) · Item #195271** · 1/4 ct tw French-cut pavé in platinum. The combination of French-cut stone exposure and platinum's color neutrality makes this the correct choice for D–G centers where every visual element should work in concert.

**[Milgrain Lace Pavé Vintage-Style 14K Rose Gold — $2,650](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/milgrain-lace-pave-vintage-style-engagement-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-by-james-allen-item-315056?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) · Item #315056** · The milgrain bead border is Blue Nile's most distinctive executed setting style — the lace-edge metalwork reads as genuinely vintage and custom at a price point significantly below independent jewelers. For buyers wanting something visually unique, this is the correct choice.

