erence begins to be visible face-up at this size. Platinum only.</td></tr><tr><td><strong><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29017695?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews">F-VVS1 Excellent</a></strong></td><td>29017695</td><td>$84,710</td><td>~$85,540</td><td>$36,000 over G-VS2 floor. Collector-tier at 3ct.</td></tr></tbody></table>

